		{"id":"bb811e78af59414b","x":-1072,"y":1212,"width":490,"height":243,"type":"text","text":"从我们有能力储存文字数据, 图像数据, 视频数据, 再到今天我们有能力储存3D云点数据,  这种进步改变了人们体验和记忆事件方式\nFrom our ability to store text data, image data, video data, and today we have the ability to store 3D cloud point data, this advancement has changed the way people experience and remember events. Therefore, what highlights can we find in this sentence to develop some interesting thesis topics\n"}
